{"tid":1824773,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北區醫院內遭三警虐待 六旬漢入稟指構成酷刑索償","createTime":"2020-01-14T16:42:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T05:59:35.000Z","uid":92301,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"501d69103cd5885f04eef2ca73a90ee489a16d72","tid":1824773,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T16:42:11.000Z","msg":"六旬漢去年在北區醫院留醫期間，在病床上遭三名警員同時毆打虐待，閉路電視拍下他受虐過程。事後三名警員被刑事檢控，案件將於本月答辯之際，傷者昨入稟區域法院，循民事途徑向三人索償，指三警的不法行為構成酷刑。<br />\n<br />\n原告為62歲的鍾姓事主，被告依序為歐國偉（25歲）、鄧文謙（24歲）、林易昇（30歲），而警務處處長暫未被列為被告。案件排期今年7月10日作簡短聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n律師林洋鋐撰寫的入稟狀指，三名被告各自或共同地於2019年6月26日，在北區醫院紊亂病人休息室7A內，對原告施加侵權及非法的武力，構成侵權及違法行為、酷刑，或公職人員行為失當。原告就此申索人身受傷的賠償。<br />\n<br />\n入稟狀續指，原告要求法庭宣告，三警行為違反原告享有人身自由及人身安全的憲制權利，以及原告不接受虐待、殘忍、不人道及侮辱性對待的權利，違反普通法、《基本法》第28條及第39條、以及《香港人權法案》第3條、第5(1)條及第6(1)條。<br />\n<br />\n刑事程序方面，三警早前被控在公職中行為失當罪，以及交替性質的襲擊致造成身體傷害罪，三人均獲保釋至本月23日往區域法院答辯。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20200114/60482872?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200114%2F60482872%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSersRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=f7d5c405\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200114%2F60482872%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=f33fdd21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20200114/60482872?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"9a0b2455346e1d695bfbee02ae8e60e47e7d503c","tid":1824773,"uid":321709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T16:45:00.000Z","msg":"禮拜五講座，手足們唔該幫推置頂<br />\n<br />\n【行動post】【吳敏兒和你組工會】1月17日（五）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1824528\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1824528</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"784aa8e7a5955dda127a8d541d994d37ecc62bc0","tid":1824773,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T16:45:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4292fc979679ed39446a3fbe4936b0d3ccf41fd8","tid":1824773,"uid":67292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T16:45:32.000Z","msg":"推到黑警仆街"},{"pid":"5b9c3c4a999b98c9f981b9497911933e05925e7b","tid":1824773,"uid":206594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T16:46:13.000Z","msg":"有險可守<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f982eaa8e978ec239f35984b2ffbfec4cf2b1f","tid":1824773,"uid":173844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T16:48:31.000Z","msg":"推到黑警冚家產<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04635512c9870569eea42df48b47e605b3dd8eee","tid":1824773,"uid":343997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T16:49:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73fe9675d4f57f93ea730dc6f46f7b9c35c4f17f","tid":1824773,"uid":230298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T16:50:06.000Z","msg":"排期今年7月10日作簡短聆訊。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n???????????????????/"},{"pid":"11c3fd357e1fd03310a0fd7801dcd75d01a7a211","tid":1824773,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T16:50:22.000Z","msg":"文宣材料唔應該只局限於「紙」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1824754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1824754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7188f5f5cee3b62778873dfd38294e62da222138","tid":1824773,"uid":88743,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T16:51:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BarB9E2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\